description:
A beautiful, cross-platform 2FA TOTP client written in Flutter
Secur is a beautiful and Secure TOTP client app for 2FA, written in Flutter. All of your TOTP secrets are stored and encrypted on-device with strong AES256 encryption. Support for being able to sync secrets to the cloud is planned and will be added in the future.

Want to collaborate or report a bug?
https://gitlab.com/ATechnoHazard/secur
